**Query #2**

    -- 2. Find employees who belong to the same department as 'Alice'
    SELECT name, department_id 
    FROM Employees 
    WHERE department_id = (
        SELECT department_id 
        FROM Employees 
        WHERE name = 'Alice'
    );

| name    | department_id |
| ------- | ------------- |
| Alice   | 101           |
| Charlie | 101           |

