**Query #4**

    -- 4. Find employees who have placed at least one order
    select emp_id,name
    from Employees
    where emp_id  IN(select emp_id from Orders);

| emp_id | name    |
| ------ | ------- |
| 1      | Alice   |
| 2      | Bob     |
| 3      | Charlie |
| 4      | David   |

